  <steps>
    <step order="1">Verify tasks 084–092 all ✅ completed. If any pending, STOP.</step>
    <step order="2">Invoke `/doc-drift-audit` skill on the repo. Capture results.</step>
    <step order="3">Grep manually for known retirement targets (skill-independent verification):
      - `grep -r "sprk_communication_send" .` (excluding `.git`) — expect zero hits in non-historical contexts
      - `grep -r "email-to-document-architecture" docs/` — expect only retirement-banner-aware references
      - `grep -r "email-to-document-automation" docs/` — same
      - `grep -r "sprk_email" docs/architecture/sdap-overview.md` — expect zero stale field refs
    </step>
    <step order="4">For each orphan found: classify (a) reference to deleted source file, (b) reference to retired doc as-canonical, (c) stale field name, (d) outdated pattern reference. List each with proposed fix.</step>
    <step order="5">Apply fixes. For docs touched by other Wave 6 tasks, prefer minor edits over wholesale rewrite.</step>
    <step order="6">Re-run `/doc-drift-audit` to confirm no remaining orphans.</step>
    <step order="7">Document the audit in `notes/research/093-doc-drift-audit.md`:
